unittitle_ssm: Photographs of Anchor Laundry in Park Slope
abstract_ssm: The Photographs of Anchor Laundry in Park Slope shows exterior and interview views of Anchor Laundry that was located on Prospect Avenue in the Park Slope neighborhood of Brooklyn, circa 1925. The collection includes group portraits of Anchor Laundry employees, as well as interior views showing employees while working.
